OL,5,G0230 FIFA World Cup 2026
OL,6,     FColombia v DR Congo (Kick-off
OL,7,     F3.00am). Laura Woods presents all
OL,8,     Fthe action from both teams' second
OL,9,     Fmatch in Group K, held at
OL,10,     FGuadalajara Stadium in Mexico. The
OL,11,     FColombians have reached the
OL,12,     Fknockout stage on three of the six
OL,13,     Foccasions they have qualified for
OL,14,     Fthe finals, including their most
OL,15,     Frecent appearance in 2018. Having
OL,16,     Ffaced Uzbekistan in their opening
OL,17,     Fgroup contest, they will be
OL,18,     Flooking to secure a place in the
OL,19,     Flast 32 here before a final-game
OL,20,     Fshowdown with Portugal. However,
OL,21,     Fthey can take nothing for granted
OL,22,     Fagainst the talented African
